00:53:15.459 --> 00:53:16.100
And I agree.

00:53:16.580 --> 00:53:22.580
I – Keith and I have been talking about, like, hey, you know, the word science and

00:53:22.580 --> 00:53:25.620
scientist is in data science and data scientist.

00:53:25.620 --> 00:53:28.260
Wouldn't it be great if we could do some science in our roles?

00:53:28.979 --> 00:53:31.620
